<div class="container-fluid">
    <p>TWIST, or Teen Women in Science and Technology, is a one-day conference to expose teen women across the state to various career possibilities.
            TWIST was developed by K-State Polytechnic and the Salina community more than 25 years ago. </p>
</div>
<div class="container-fluid">
    <div class='row'>
        <p>Use the following form to add a new Topic</p>
    </div>
</div>
<form action="/catalog/Topic/{{_id}}/update" method="POST">
	<input name="_id" type="hidden" id="_id" value={{_id}}>
	<label for="topicCode">TopicCode:</label><br>
	<input name="topicCode" type="text" id="topicCode" value="{{topicCode}}"><br><br>
	<label for="title">Title:</label><br>
	<input name="title" type="text" id="title" value="{{title}}"><br><br>
	<label for="description">Description:</label><br>
	<input name="description" type="text" id="description" value="{{description}}"><br><br>
	<input type="submit" value="Add Topic"><br>
</form>
{{#if errors}}
    {{#each errors}}
	<p>{{this.msg}}</p>
	{{/each}}
	{{/if}}